{"tid":2462334,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"理性和心理質素比正面思考更重要，你同意嗎？","createTime":"2021-03-26T02:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T13:39:55.000Z","uid":177089,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ee2fadb6e6080609957f8bee8e7242b93c9bf0","tid":2462334,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"正面思考只係左膠思維 唔睇清現實<br />\n純粹以「正面=好」立於不敗之地<br />\n實際上並唔會解決問題 只係解決心態問題<br />\n<br />\n強健嘅心理質素先係一個人需要嘅特質<br />\n唔單單係向正面思考 而係即使面臨逆境 <br />\n仍然能夠承受 以理性去思考解決方法<br />\n最後令問題實際得到解決<br />\n<br />\n正面思考法只係廢人用嚟逃避現實<br />\n係一種心靈上嘅自慰 特別係啲蠢女人最鍾意用<br />\n仲要四圍推廣 將正面當成美德 見到就覺得噁心"},{"pid":"0941c5e3b19c79693cf08e0b1342775a1758145b","tid":2462334,"uid":287107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:09:16.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40107a006d19c43a348c82d6b14243a238021afa","tid":2462334,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:17:05.000Z","msg":"好妒忌啲happy idiots"},{"pid":"65e92dcb21a5c4950b092fa655fb35d12464ef5d","tid":2462334,"uid":129676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cc83e2fe05ca8d50e94a4e1ff615a5a1b120fe","tid":2462334,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:19:53.000Z","msg":"啲明星日日貼啲正撚量po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4af2eb09148a062f66eb20862cf746087d9edb","tid":2462334,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:46:22.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過所有問題都係心態問題？<br />\n有人咸魚青菜就滿足<br />\n有人發揮理性，揾好多錢，食omakase<br />\n有人活五六十年就無憾<br />\n有人發揮理性，揾好多錢，食靚藥吊命做人瑞"},{"pid":"f7609d90615a480b61bfd133c4480d01e5a2b236","tid":2462334,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f4af2eb09148a062f66eb20862cf746087d9edb","tid":2462334,"uid":286